        "TileImage": "$($repository fa0b9f07-d667-48d2-99c0-c5ee905fa973).Image",
        "Description": "Patrick and the family buttler, Mr. Fernsby are planning to take off with the inheritence after Alexa Carlise died. Hearing of this, Alexa set up her death for her own reasons and to flush out these two. Panicing, they called you to kill what was supposed to be a dead women. Unbeknownst to them, Alexa had already called you knowing they would try any means to get rid of her, and hiring guards around the property made it the better choice for them to call you.\r\rYou know what to do.",
